                "name": "Soul Chains",
                "type": "section",
                "sections": [],
                "text": "A forge-spurned wields a soul chain: a cursed <i>+1 <a aonid=\"280\" game-obj=\"Equipment\">striking</a> <a aonid=\"295\" game-obj=\"Equipment\">flaming</a> <a aonid=\"60\" game-obj=\"Weapons\">spiked chain</a></i>. Any other creature that has a <i>soul chain</i> must succeed at a DC 22 Will save each day at sundown or transform into a forge-spurned permanently. A forge-spurned stops at nothing to retrieve its <i>soul chain</i> if it\u2019s lost.",
