                {
                    "name": "Soul Chain",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "If a creature is slain by an attack from the <i>soul chain</i> and the forge-spurned is able to retain the creature\u2019s corpse, it can bind the creature\u2019s soul into the <i>soul chain</i> (as <a aonid=\"21\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>bind soul</i></a>) with a day of work at a forge and a successful DC 20 <a aonid=\"4\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Crafting</a> check. An individual whose soul is bound in this way can\u2019t be resurrected unless the soul chain is destroyed (Hardness 5, HP 20, BT 10).",
